    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no dings, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine, featuring leather that remains supple and an interior that still retains its new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, providing a smooth, powerful, and whisper-quiet driving experience with all systems functioning exactly as designed. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained example that requires absolutely nothing but a new driver.",
