    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This car is looking for a new owner ready to give it some serious TLC. While it's currently in poor condition and will need significant repairs and restoration to get back to its best, it offers a great foundation for anyone looking for a rewarding mechanical project. Grab this diamond in the rough at a fantastic price and make it your own!",
