    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs smoothly and looks great\u2014ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
